value.0: This halfling has a hard, uncompromising look in her eyes. The clothes she wears and her general bearing indicate a successful merchant. There is also a pride in her bearing as she touches her merchandise.
This commoner lacks the haggard look common among people of other districts.
This child seems happy enough, probably from being shielded from the horrors of the plague, or from being simply too young to understand.
